{
  "stem": "8784.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if I look at the route that this group took from Brunnlitz to go to Krakow, we went north instead of heading east all the time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we really did not know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were not prepared intellectually, mentally to do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But nevertheless, a group of 17 people-- 4 ladies and 13 men-- banded together after a few days after the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We banded together with the expressed purpose of reaching Krakow, Poland to see whether any of our relatives remained alive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was our-- We did not know much about our will to stay in Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had an idea that we don't, but nevertheless, we felt that this was our obligation is to get back to Krakow, Poland and begin to see if any of the relatives remained alive.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the 17 of us took risks, because we are now supposed to be going in Czechoslovakia heading eastward.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Russian army is marching westward.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they are greeting us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As they are going one way, we are going the other way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The way-- the only way we can make it to get to Krakow was on-- on foot and rounding up some horses.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is the end of the war, and there were some stray horses roaming the fields.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were able to round up some of those horses that were limping a little bit or were not in the best of shape.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But nevertheless, they would be good enough for us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would hitch them up to a wagon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And now we had those bundles that Oskar Schindler left for us in the warehouses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we-- 17 of us would load up those bundles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some of us that were weaker would be on the wagon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some of us would walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
